{"id":262945,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/11/维权网-广西南宁十八大期间强征土地（图）/","date":"2012-11-14T02:16:06Z","modified":"2012-11-14T02:16:06Z","title":"维权网 | 广西南宁“十八大”期间强征土地（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><b><span>（维权网信息员张歆怡报道）</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>日</span><span>，广西南宁市良庆区那黄村发生一起强征土地事件，大片山林被捣毁。此次征地的面积约为<span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span>亩，当地村民四年前在该地块上栽种桉树，大部分树木已经成材。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据当地村民韦先生介绍，当天早上<span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span>时许，<span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span>多名身着迷彩警服的征地人员到达该村。领头的是五象新区指挥部官员杜家元，和良庆区征地拆迁办公室征地五组副组长龚礼千。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>征地人员拉起警戒线，几台大型钩机进入地块，强行捣毁桉树。数十名村名试图阻止，双方短暂争执，但没有发生肢体冲突。至中午时分，<span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span>亩桉树林全部被推倒。期间，村民多次要求出示征地手续，但征地人员并未理睬。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据本网信息员了解，此次强征行动并未事先通知村民。村民在一个月前才接到政府人员的口头通知，称要以每亩<span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span>万多元的价格征收该地块，用于修建五象新区道路。由于补偿是按<span lang=\"EN-US\">2008</span>年的标准，价格偏低，加上没有任何安置，所以村民一直没有与政府签署协议。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>另外，强征行动结束不久，村民拨打<span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span>报警，<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>个多小时后警察才到达现场，在得知是政府所为后即匆匆离去。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>当地村民韦其松：<span lang=\"EN-US\">13077772147</span></span></div>\n<div><span>当地村民韦吉少：<span lang=\"EN-US\">15978185009</span></span></div>\n<div><span>五象新区指挥部官员杜家元：<span lang=\"EN-US\">13877121933</span></span></div>\n<div><span>良庆区拆迁办征地五组副组长龚礼千：<span lang=\"EN-US\">13978794478</span></span></div>\n<div><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-N_KkJxFkfxA/UKL4eryHgNI/AAAAAAAATbg/A0O1lS6zVUU/s1600/72072-1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"213\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-N_KkJxFkfxA/UKL4eryHgNI/AAAAAAAATbg/A0O1lS6zVUU/s320/72072-1.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-nGZfAO_nQF0/UKL4liQiTDI/AAAAAAAATbo/SzCYJQApYqM/s1600/72072-2.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"213\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-nGZfAO_nQF0/UKL4liQiTDI/AAAAAAAATbo/SzCYJQApYqM/s320/72072-2.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div></div>\n<div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-xWQN2U1ynEg/UKL4sCoa8RI/AAAAAAAATbw/wvmTpbkvdtM/s1600/72072-3.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"213\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-xWQN2U1ynEg/UKL4sCoa8RI/AAAAAAAATbw/wvmTpbkvdtM/s320/72072-3.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-3657511546176224665?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}